Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.82,0:00:08.10,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Pega?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.86,0:00:11.57,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:20.33,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... the Sky Sea is too quiet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:25.14,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen to \Nthe Priestess of the Sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:02:00.55,DogDays-ep-title,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)\an3}The Star Whale in the Sky Sea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.81,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Adel-sama and her friend's
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:04.06,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,adventures were amazing, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:04.94,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:07.31,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,It was truly a heroic tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:10.15,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,They saved the world and changed the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:12.19,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,when they were about our age.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:14.93,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Risking their own lives, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:15.69,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:18.03,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,We need to be like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:22.32,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,We need to bring good things not just \Nto our own country, but to the continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:23.33,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:25.66,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Leo-nee! Nanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:27.50,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.58,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.21,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.46,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are Shinku and Leaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.88,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Practicing swordsmanship, I'm told.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:37.21,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Gaul went with them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.84,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,They can't interfere with us girls talking,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.59,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,supposedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:44.15,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:49.48,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:50.85,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:06.87,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,The priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:08.50,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,And the fire dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:09.75,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:13.13,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Leaders of the three countries! Heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:15.63,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to appear so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.83,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Would you hear what I have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:24.43,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,The Sky Sea has been acting \Nstrange since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.60,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,The Sky Sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:28.91,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,You need a simple explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:31.54,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,And me and Rebecca are the \Nperfect ones to give it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:33.94,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,We just studied it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:35.32,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:39.04,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,There's a sea called the Sky Sea \Nabove Flognarde's skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.57,DogDays-main,Co,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sea, but that doesn't \Nmean there's water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:44.25,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,The space between the floating \Nislands and the clouds,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:46.89,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,and the creatures and \Nspirits that live there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:49.97,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,They're born in the Sky Sea, \Nand sleep in the Sky Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:53.14,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,There's a mysterious and \Nwonderful ecology up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:57.46,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,There are no countries or \Nterritory in the Sky Sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:03:59.96,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,but there's something there that \Nis in charge of the peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.03,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the star whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:05.72,DogDays-main,Co,0000,0000,0000,,A huge flying spirit, \Nbigger than a mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.47,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We surface academics call it a spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:10.30,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,but there are also theories that it's
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:13.27,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,the servant of an ancient god,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:16.23,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,or a type of dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:19.89,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's older than people, of course, but \Nit's also older than the True Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:23.89,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The Star Whale has lived in \NFlognarde for a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:25.66,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Several times a year, you can see it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.24,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,swimming in the sky from the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:32.91,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And so, just like there's a Dragon Priestess \Nthat connects the people and the dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:37.09,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,there is a Sky Priestess who connects \Nthe Star Whale and the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:38.63,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,it's said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:40.77,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens above the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:43.76,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,the Sky Priestess will tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:45.13,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:48.14,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the Sky Priestess is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:50.20,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,just a story in picture books.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:53.39,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows if she exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:55.89,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a romantic story, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:58.38,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell how the weather \Nand temperature will change by
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:00.51,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,looking at the movement of the \Nstars and the state of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:03.78,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,That might be where the legend comes from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.03,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:08.53,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Um... the Sky Priestess is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:11.46,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I've met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:12.62,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:18.29,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Pega is a messenger from the stars, \Ncreated by the Sky Priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:19.42,DogDays-main,Co,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.54,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:24.17,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Pega tells me something might've \Nhappened to the Sky Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:28.09,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It might be to the environment where the \NStar Whale lives, or to the Star Whale itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.68,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,or maybe to the Sky Priestess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:33.45,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to go see what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:37.42,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,The Star Whale is above these \Nthree countries right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:41.32,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like permission from you \Nto investigate your skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:42.57,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.07,DogDays-main,Co,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:46.07,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,No problem, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:48.78,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're going alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:51.56,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going on a sky \Nadventure, we'll follow you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:53.83,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be great to have around in \Nan investigation or an adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.83,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.96,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Dragon Priestess's job,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.46,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,but it would good to have \Nthe Heroes along, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:03.62,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:06.97,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Then Couver, Milfi, shall we go, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:07.72,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:09.36,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.60,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Is what I'd like to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:16.48,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a bunch of work I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:18.73,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's true for all three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:20.35,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.61,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,You guys can stay in your countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.61,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Hero's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:26.61,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:28.74,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It would be better to \Nhave more people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:30.92,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll need a researcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:33.12,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Onmitsu will be useful, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:37.37,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Then the members will be the \Npriestess, the three Heroes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:40.50,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Genoise, Rico, and Yukikaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:43.75,DogDays-main,Ga,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Leaf and I will go,\N too. It's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:44.81,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:47.38,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,You're going as a representative \Nof Galette, Gaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:48.26,DogDays-main,Ga,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:52.39,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Leaf, use your bow \Nand ears to help everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:53.39,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.26,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Um... which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:56.17,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:59.69,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,A problem with the Sky Sea is a problem \Nnot just for our three countries,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.40,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,but for the whole continent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:04.15,DogDays-main,Co,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be ready to go,\N if there's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:07.86,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll have the priestess \Nlead a team to investigate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:08.93,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:09.65,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.92,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Sky Sea investigation team!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:27.85,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Off we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:36.47,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.18,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let go of the ropes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:39.06,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.61,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Rico, what's in the box?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:47.57,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,A box of secret machines I prepared \Nwith the people of Pastillage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:51.19,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's filled with useful items \Nto help with the investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:52.65,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:53.57,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:03.58,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like being on a plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.46,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:06.58,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The humidity's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.84,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Clouds are clumped up \Nwater vapor, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:13.55,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the fire dragon \Ndoesn't like the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.08,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get out of the clouds quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.09,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:20.83,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.10,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I think!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:25.35,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Our trip to the Sky Sea is a little rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:28.61,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to flying, so I'm still okay, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.36,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost out of the clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:53.80,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Sky Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:56.43,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen it before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:58.55,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.92,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:00.60,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:05.04,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Pictures! Pictures! I need to take pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:05.48,DogDays-overlap,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:07.60,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,So where's the Star Whale?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:09.98,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it. It's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.02,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:24.19,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It's even bigger up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:27.22,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:29.63,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, its color is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:31.43,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:33.64,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, it shines more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:35.76,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty, like the starry sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:37.76,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Is it sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:39.89,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:43.50,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,If we meet the priestess \Nwe can talk to her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.27,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:46.77,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the Star Whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:49.90,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,We're going inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:52.98,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I remember how to get to \Nwhere the priestess is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.47,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:56.36,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it going to eat us by accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.38,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:10:00.43,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,From the Star Whale's perspective,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.18,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,even the fire dragon's the \Nsize of a grain of dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:04.04,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,And I've heard
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:06.37,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,it almost never eats anything anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.50,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:10.63,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I'm still scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.95,0:10:11.93,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:14.87,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,With the fire dragon's wings, \Nit will just take a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:17.27,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,It really is huge, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.27,0:10:19.95,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how many times bigger \Nit is than an Earth whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.07,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:24.89,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:25.77,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:34.15,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um... it's opening its mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:36.03,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do? Get a little further back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.32,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that would be a good—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:46.71,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is it sucking us in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:47.95,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:49.58,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Fire dragon, get us out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.24,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Rico!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:10:58.59,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:10:59.34,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Rico!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:45.10,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we... Everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:48.72,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That was awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:52.09,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we got separated \Nfrom the people of Galette.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:54.73,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:57.45,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the star whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:00.74,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't look like the \Ninside of a living thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:04.49,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's dark, I'm surprised \Nthere's any light at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:07.16,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of light spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:10.75,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, it's a lot brighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:14.01,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's find Gaul and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:15.63,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Brave Connect, on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:20.02,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Becky! Shinku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:21.01,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.67,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Nanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:23.88,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Who's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:25.86,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,This is what we've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:29.14,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,We protected Rico-yan's secret \Nbox of machines with our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.89,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:33.01,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul's not with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:34.27,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We got separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:35.53,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:38.83,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul-kun hung in there until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:41.65,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he's at least with the fire dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:44.28,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul has a hero crystal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:46.53,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The crystals can call to one another...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:50.91,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about the Star Whale, but first \Nwe need to meet up with the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:52.23,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:07.48,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:24.89,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:26.77,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I was sucked in and fell into the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:31.61,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:34.57,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed I survived even \Nthough I was out cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:37.11,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm just that good... maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:44.01,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Forest people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:46.26,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,No... they're a different color.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:47.84,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,The spirits here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:50.55,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:54.10,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be leaving soon, so don't be so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:08.36,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Um... who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:12.74,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Can I use this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:22.75,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.14,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,It's so warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.97,0:14:27.09,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Did you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:30.75,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,save me when I was drowning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:32.34,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:33.87,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from Galette.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.14,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget what you did for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:36.57,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:41.02,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,So can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:46.50,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:48.40,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I should dry my clothes off, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:53.91,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,So we're inside the Sky Whale, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:55.32,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.12,DogDays-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:02.29,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just speak directly inside my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.51,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:08.49,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...  I just thought \Nit was a pretty voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:09.93,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,and it startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.91,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Do you live here, Aria?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:15.59,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:17.18,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Then who are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:20.81,DogDays-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,The Sky People. They're my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:22.56,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any other people here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:25.07,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:28.56,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Did you lose your memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:35.73,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,You might've gotten sucked in, too, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:39.32,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,You see, we've come from the surface
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:41.39,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,to check on the Star Whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:45.08,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We think something might've \Nhappened in the Sky Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:49.96,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,And so I came to see the Sky \NPriestess with my friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:54.14,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,but when the Star Whale sucked \Nus in I got separated from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:56.60,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about this, Aria?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:16:00.12,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,About the Star Whale, or the Sky Priestess?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:04.17,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:07.62,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Once my clothes dry, I'll go find my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:14.24,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:17.78,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,It must be lonely being here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:21.62,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,As a representative of Galette, \NI'll take good care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:24.50,DogDays-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.23,DogDays-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:31.54,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul's signal is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:34.26,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're a good ways \Napart from each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.01,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,What about your end, Nanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:39.26,DogDays-internal,N,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I'm closer. \NThe crystal is responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.51,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:42.02,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Answer us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:46.22,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The Priestess must know we're inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:48.27,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,And the Star Whale should know, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:51.40,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, they'd speak to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:53.90,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,The Star Whale talks, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:57.16,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't necessarily talk... \Nyou can hear it's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:00.99,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,If the priestess is with you, she can \Ntranslate it into human language
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.79,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,to make it easier to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:05.04,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't quite understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:08.42,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,but if we find the priestess we should be \Nable to talk to it about things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:12.46,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,We need to find Gaul-kun, \Nand meet the Sky Priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:15.54,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he's safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:18.43,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Something was just moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:24.39,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:25.12,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:28.56,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe there are \Ndemons inside the sky whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:34.83,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Mercurius!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:42.30,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:43.70,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to attack us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:54.30,DogDays-main,K,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fight our way through! \NLet's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:54.90,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:55.59,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:56.59,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:02.03,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,These aren't demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:03.45,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,They're not animals, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:04.85,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Then what are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:06.62,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:09.73,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But they're like bacteria \Nor microscopic organisms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:12.05,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight our way through!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:13.96,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Vert and I will make a path!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:19.25,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:20.07,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:24.41,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,This sound... Nanami, \NNoir and the others are fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:26.16,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:27.61,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:28.71,DogDays-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:30.46,DogDays-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's extremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:34.63,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried about me? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:37.67,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,But my friends are fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:39.20,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go help...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:44.21,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what you meant by dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:46.70,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Those are monsters with no definite form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:48.48,DogDays-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,Those are Sickness Demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:52.86,DogDays-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,They make the Star Whale \Nsick and bring disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.42,DogDays-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,Bad creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:55.67,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:18:58.96,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Which means I can kick the \Ncrap out of them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.96,0:19:00.00,DogDays-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:02.74,DogDays-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,They're very strong and \Nthere are a lot of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:04.29,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:07.20,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Then we just have to defeat them and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:09.62,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,go forward so we don't get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:18.38,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Lion King Lightning Circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:29.58,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go, Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:32.56,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I'll introduce you to my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:43.32,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,We defeated a lot, \Nbut there's no end to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:46.24,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's like when we fought the dragon eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:48.64,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It was just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:50.90,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Are these things why
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:53.21,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,the Star Whale isn't feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.58,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:56.53,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:57.09,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:58.71,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's Prince Gaul's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.46,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:06.22,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.97,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.60,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Gaul! You're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:16.12,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:17.75,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul-kun! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:19.73,DogDays-internal,G,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.78,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Prince. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:24.02,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,We know where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:27.74,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I found a path I took when \NI met the Priestess last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:31.03,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading to her throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:34.25,DogDays-internal,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to find the Fire Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.61,0:20:35.52,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:38.11,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It's lost, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:40.55,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,It would be bad if it was attacked \Nby the Sickness Demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.13,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We need to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:43.33,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sickness Demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:45.77,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,That's what those things that \Nlook like demons are called.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:47.70,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Aria told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:50.27,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Aria?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:52.64,DogDays-internal,G,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know her either, then, Sharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:54.95,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:56.34,DogDays-internal,G,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she's lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.65,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,She can't remember why she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:00.84,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:11.46,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:13.41,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen to the priestess?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:19.41,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Priestess! Sky Priestess Farine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:21.67,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sharu, the Dragon Priestess! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:44.44,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Priestess! I'm glad! You're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.35,0:21:48.96,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:50.69,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Things are getting
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:53.62,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,a little difficult here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.13,0:23:34.67,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,The Priestess Farine is \None of the local gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.67,0:23:36.19,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,She's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.19,0:23:37.83,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:40.09,DogDays-next-ep-title long,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)}The Sky Priestess and the Star People
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.13,0:23:39.70,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,See you next time.
